-- Microsoft's Chief Software Architect Ray Ozzie to Step Down
-- B y   D i n a   B a s s
-- 2010-10-18T20:48:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-18/microsoft-chief-software-architect-ray-ozzie-to-step-down-shares-decline.html
Microsoft Corp. Chief Software
Architect Ray Ozzie is stepping down.  Ozzie, who joined the company in 2005, will be “on board”
for a while before departing, Chief Executive Officer Steve
Ballmer said today in an e-mail on the company’s website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Dina Bass in Seattle at 
